So we'll take about five or
six minutes of questions,

00:44:28.820 --> 00:44:29.930
show the final slide show.

00:44:29.930 --> 00:44:31.763
And then if you all are
interested in books,

00:44:31.763 --> 00:44:34.920
Google has them available
at a discount for $10.

00:44:34.920 --> 00:44:36.930
And we're happy to sign
those for you as well.

